Write a detailed store description (separate from manifest description)
Choose relevant categories
If you create a landing page:
Add Open Graph tags for social sharing
Create content about the problem it solves
Consider a simple GitHub Pages site
Update the homepage URL:
Replace "https://github.com/yourusername/shortsban" with your actual repository or website URL
The code is now optimized for discoverability. The manifest description will help with store search rankings.

